Title: Final Destination 5
Actors: Nicholas D'Agosto, Emma Bell, Miles Fisher, Ellen Wroe
Plot: In this latest installment to the horror franchise, Sam and his friends manages to escape a ill-fated bridge, thanks to a premonition Sam obtained. However, when two of his friends died in a mysterious way, Sam must use his memories from the premonition to save his friends, before death hunts him down.
